    "Research on journal indexing systems, citation metrics, journal quality frameworks, database governance and transparency, and open scholarly infrastructure for evaluation.": "研究期刊索引系统、引文指标、期刊质量框架、数据库治理与透明度，以及用于评价的开放学术基础设施。",
    "Research on higher education policy, science and innovation governance, social governance, digital governance, and the policy dimensions of scholarly communication.": "研究高等教育政策、科学与创新治理、社会治理、数字治理，以及学术传播的政策维度。",
