    "Responsible for the editorial management, production, and open access dissemination of all Institute publications, including research reports, working papers, policy briefs, edited volumes, and the annual report.": "负责本院所有出版成果的编辑管理、制作和开放获取传播，包括研究报告、工作论文、政策简报、主编文集和年度报告。",
