    "Responsible for managing the Institute's external partnerships, institutional cooperation agreements, research project proposals, edited volume proposals, and event co-organization inquiries.": "负责管理本院外部伙伴关系、机构合作协议、研究项目提案、主编文集提案和活动联合组织咨询。",
    "The Institute is governed through the following structure. All governance activities are conducted in accordance with this Charter and with the overarching governance framework of Panorama Scholarly Group.": "本院通过以下结构进行治理。所有治理活动均依照本章程和全景学术集团总体治理框架开展。",
    "Institute Director": "研究院院长",
